name: "Muhammad Ali" circa 1964
description: “I’m the most talked-about, most publicized, the most famous, and the most colorful fighter in history. And I’m the fastest heavyweight — with feet and hands — who ever lived. Besides that, I’m the onliest poet laureate boxing’s ever had. One other thing, too: If you look at pictures of all the former champions you know in a flash that I’m the best-looking champion in history. It all adds up to being The Greatest, don’t it?” - Ali
